sequenceDiagram
  participant Dev as Wearable/Sim
  participant MQ as MQTT Broker
  participant S as Python Server
  participant C as Contacts

  Dev->>MQ: publish wearable/{id}/sos
  MQ-->>S: forward SOS
  S->>Dev: publish wearable/{id}/ack
  S->>C: Send SMS (Twilio)
  S->>C: Optional Voice Call


